spirit:field.spirit:name: Write_Data
spirit:field.spirit:description: Write register to send data to the other interface.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RDDATA
spirit:field.spirit:description: Read register to get data word sent from the other interface.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Empty
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates current status of the interface in the receive direction: 0 - There is data available. 1 - The FIFO is empty.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Full
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates current status of the interface in the send direction: 0 - There is room for more data. 1 - The FIFO is full.

spirit:field.spirit:name: STA
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates current FIFO status of the interface in the send direction: 0 - Send FIFO level is greater than the SIT threshold. 1 - Send FIFO level is less than or equal to the SIT threshold.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RTA
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates current FIFO status of the interface in the receive direction: 0 - Receive FIFO level is less than or equal to the RIT threshold. 1 - Receive FIFO level is greater than the RIT threshold.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Empty_Error
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates attempts to read from RDDATA with Empty flag set: 0 - No error has occurred. 1 - Attempts to read while FIFO is empty. Cleared on read.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Full_Error
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates attempts to write to WRDATA with Full flag set: 0 - No error has occurred. 1 - Attempts to write while FIFO is full. Cleared on read.

spirit:field.spirit:name: SIT
spirit:field.spirit:description: Contains interrupt threshold for the interface in send direction.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RIT
spirit:field.spirit:description: Contains interrupt threshold for the interface in receive direction.

spirit:field.spirit:name: STI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Send Threshold Interrupt for the interface: 0 - No interrupt event has occurred. 1 - Data level in send FIFO has caused a STI.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RTI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Receive Threshold Interrupt for the interface: 0 - No interrupt event has occurred. 1 - Data level in receive FIFO has caused a RTI.

spirit:field.spirit:name: ERR
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Error Interrupt Status for the interface: 0 - No interrupt event has occurred. 1 - A Mailbox error has occurred.

spirit:field.spirit:name: STI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Send Threshold Interrupt Enable for the interface: 0 - STI interrupt is disabled. 1 - STI interrupt is enabled.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RTI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Receive Threshold Interrupt Enable for the interface: 0 - RTI interrupt is disabled. 1 - RTI interrupt is enabled.

spirit:field.spirit:name: ERR
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Error Interrupt Enable for the interface: 0 - ERR interrupt is disabled. 1 - ERR interrupt is enabled.

spirit:field.spirit:name: STI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Send Threshold Interrupt Pending status for the interface: 0 - No pending interrupt. 1 - Pending interrupt for data level in send FIFO.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RTI
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Receive Threshold Interrupt Pending status for the interface: 0 - No pending interrupt. 1 - Pending interrupt for data level in receive FIFO.

spirit:field.spirit:name: ERR
spirit:field.spirit:description: Mailbox Error Interrupt Pending status for the interface: 0 - No pending interrupt. 1 - Pending interrupt for Mailbox errors.

spirit:field.spirit:name: CSF
spirit:field.spirit:description: Clear send FIFO for the interface: 0 - Do nothing. 1 - Clear the send FIFO.

spirit:field.spirit:name: CRF
spirit:field.spirit:description: Clear receive FIFO for the interface: 0 - Do nothing. 1 - Clear the receive FIFO.
